{{Wikipedia category|tracking=yes|container=yes|
This category contains all the categories about '''[[Wikipedia:Redirect|redirects]]'''.This category should not contain any redirects itself; there are so many of them that a category of them all would be unmanageable. However, certain kinds of redirect are categorized by type—for example, [[:Category:Redirects from misspellings|redirects from misspellings]].
For a list of templates that can be applied to redirect pages, see [[Wikipedia:Template messages/Redirect pages]].
}}

